{"tid":2372263,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple M1 Mac終於裝到Windows！！！","createTime":"2021-01-19T13:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T14:29:54.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"653241fe307bd650b96427fce053faf5f6af3656","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a0999a2c3247a0a953bb570d9ef661a54bf570","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"ARM版Windows10怎麼安裝？M1 Mac安裝ARM版Win10教程<br />\n<br />\nParallels最近發布了與M1 Mac兼容的Parallels 16的技術預覽，並且運行良好。Apple Silicon版本的Parallels專為基於ARM的操作系統而設計，因此它不適用於Windows 10的x86版本，而需要Windows的ARM版本。在此教程中，我們將向您展示如何使用Parallels在M1 Mac上運行ARM版Windows。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c3cd17b6c2efe028f052ceb10e9c2c6a_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-c3cd17b6c2efe028f052ceb10e9c2c6a_720w.jpg&h=447d9299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備工作<br />\n<br />\nParallels Desktop for M1 Mac軟件<br />\n<br />\n訪問<a href=\"https://b2b.parallels.com/apple-silicon進入Parallels\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fb2b.parallels.com%2Fapple-silicon%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5Parallels&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmei%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f70da791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://b2b.parallels.com/apple-silicon進入Parallels</a> Desktop技術預覽版官網，點擊尝试技术预览進入登陸頁面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a5f93cca4ea46113f8a3bf6ee07fa8f9_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-a5f93cca4ea46113f8a3bf6ee07fa8f9_720w.jpg&h=4eeec918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n選擇適合自己的登陸方式，新用戶也可以註冊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f5464a0a7bc075aeb63a9b2650fe30bf_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-f5464a0a7bc075aeb63a9b2650fe30bf_720w.jpg&h=e7f84841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就可以得到軟件的下载地址和激活码(請保留好激活碼，安裝需要用到)"},{"pid":"fc9d4c388a5de94b772994aba6c097909e491cf2","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b492ce69cf902d7ec985eea173f48d78_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-b492ce69cf902d7ec985eea173f48d78_720w.jpg&h=eacca468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWindows10 arm版系統<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://insider.windows.com/en-us/getting-started\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finsider.windows.com%2Fen-us%2Fgetting-started&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmei%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=83b13c23\" target=\"_blank\">https://insider.windows.com/en-us/getting-started</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/software-download/windowsinsiderpreviewARM64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fsoftware-download%2FwindowsinsiderpreviewARM64&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmei%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b4391c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/software-download/windowsinsiderpreviewARM64</a><br />\n<br />\n註冊Windows Insider程序，然後下載Windows 10客戶端ARM64 Insider Preview<br />\n<br />\n或者訪問https:// uupdump.ml/選擇21227 arm版本（只有21277版或更新的版本可以同時運行X86、X64、ARM架構軟件。而21277之前的版本只能運行X86和ARM。）<br />\n<br />\nPD虛擬機安裝win10教程<br />\n<br />\nPD虛擬機安裝完成後打開，點擊continue繼續<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-fd40fdc8e9909252425522a68c534ad6_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-fd40fdc8e9909252425522a68c534ad6_720w.jpg&h=247f96f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後PD虛擬機會自動掃描電腦上的windows系統，點擊Create<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-00d0c031abeb45567284eb650ea210a9_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-00d0c031abeb45567284eb650ea210a9_720w.jpg&h=40d4acc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正在創建，耐心等待幾分鐘"},{"pid":"a99765c7bc42fd376efb35b0b129485417696b52","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-9ddd7b5cc006cb2b1039b295f86ed5cd_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-9ddd7b5cc006cb2b1039b295f86ed5cd_720w.jpg&h=cbcde021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n需要登錄自己的賬戶，點擊Sign in...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-24397bf45265ef9abc684554f728ea51_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-24397bf45265ef9abc684554f728ea51_720w.jpg&h=1225a770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n需要激活碼來激活PD虛擬機，我們將上面PD官網上的註冊碼複製到指定位置，點擊Activate<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-f1a2e419085c111a4307af40813cd4de_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-f1a2e419085c111a4307af40813cd4de_720w.jpg&h=d3f5acba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提示PD虛擬機激活成功，點擊OK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-038e0d325f2057a5fa9029cce8910fad_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-038e0d325f2057a5fa9029cce8910fad_720w.jpg&h=10059552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下來靜靜的等著Win10安裝成功就可以了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-482d948dbfeeeb98d0586e85d26c7209_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-482d948dbfeeeb98d0586e85d26c7209_720w.jpg&h=2246f483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f56db1400ae4df3444bf613e0432642d4600788b","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"M1運行ARM版本的win10虛擬機效果如何<br />\n<br />\nCPU只有5%不到，而內存也只有6個多G，是不是非常香！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-863f075e6736245c8d3b8fc015a4daff_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-863f075e6736245c8d3b8fc015a4daff_720w.jpg&h=1ddd6db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-de4d08b5404532844981cf354d44c766_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-de4d08b5404532844981cf354d44c766_720w.jpg&h=1d57eb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在看來蘋果M1對Windows的兼容性非常不錯，不用再擔心M1 Mac無法運行Windows程序，而且YouTube上許多用戶上傳了用M1安裝Windows玩遊戲的視頻，並沒有發現卡頓或者風扇狂轉。"},{"pid":"628e3a7d64343a00f3079165e2e2e84df0ec41d8","tid":2372263,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"WINDOW有咩SOFTWARE係有ARM版"},{"pid":"c83769124c2c92d080d69e51341cdb48c54ce4f6","tid":2372263,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ee3c8b1e5a76cc4dd05f5caf06fa290f7c531f","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"ARM版 Windows 暫時都淨係支援x86嘅32 bits 程式<br />\n<br />\n你一用64 bits好多都會crash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac917b6e24ebe7da50b4d27c8c36325d6acda8f","tid":2372263,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"緊追蘋果！ARM 版本 Windows 10 終於推出 